title: Turkey warns Moscow over trade ties, says Russian military build-up in Syria 'unacceptable'
text:
Published By: Fox News: World - Today 
Turkish President Recep Tayyip Erdogan is warning Russia that its military action in Syria is endangering trade ties with Turkey....
